Economic possibilities for GazaIt doesn't hurt to dream of better days. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/economic-possibilities-for-gaza https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/economic-possibilities-for-gazaNoah Smith Thu, 19 Oct 2023 08:57:08 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc7ebf790-eaf4-4398-91c9-45780f5e4730_978x713.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc7ebf790-eaf4-4398-91c9-45780f5e4730_978x713.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc7ebf790-eaf4-4398-91c9-45780f5e4730_978x713.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc7ebf790-eaf4-4398-91c9-45780f5e4730_978x713.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc7ebf790-eaf4-4398-91c9-45780f5e4730_978x713.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc7ebf790-eaf4-4398-91c9-45780f5e4730_978x713.jpeg" width="978" height="713" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c7ebf790-eaf4-4398-91c9-45780f5e4730_978x713.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:713,&quot;width&quot;:978,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:227524,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc7ebf790-eaf4-4398-91c9-45780f5e4730_978x713.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc7ebf790-eaf4-4398-91c9-45780f5e4730_978x713.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc7ebf790-eaf4-4398-91c9-45780f5e4730_978x713.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc7ebf790-eaf4-4398-91c9-45780f5e4730_978x713.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></figure></div><p>幸运的是，有关以色列轰炸加沙一家医院并造成 500 人死亡的报道<a href="https://twitter.com/Nrg8000/status/1714535497958334678">被证明不是真的</a>。但 <em><a href="https://nymag.com/intelligencer/2023/10/the-undisputed-facts-in-gaza-are-enough.html">以色列</a></em><a href="https://nymag.com/intelligencer/2023/10/the-undisputed-facts-in-gaza-are-enough.html">确实</a>在该领土上投下了许多炸弹，许多无辜者已经被杀害，并且在未来的日子里还会有更多的人<a href="https://nymag.com/intelligencer/2023/10/the-undisputed-facts-in-gaza-are-enough.html">被</a>杀害。似乎很少有人关心加沙的 200 万人民——<a href="https://nymag.com/intelligencer/2023/10/what-israel-didnt-understand-about-hamas.html">哈马斯不关心</a>，他们试图挑起残酷的报复，以赢得国际社会对其事业的支持；以色列也不关心，以色列谈论集体惩罚并封锁加沙数十年；埃及或埃及也不关心。其他阿拉伯国家也<a href="https://apnews.com/article/palestinian-jordan-egypt-israel-refugee-502c06d004767d4b64848d878b66bd3d">拒绝接收加沙难民</a>。加沙人孤立无援，无国籍，基本上被整个地球抛弃。</p><p>在这样的时刻，一些人可能会认为谈论加沙的长期经济未来是轻蔑或冷漠的。也许需要《经济学人大脑》的临终案例才能看到一片陷入无休止战争的土地并说：“你知道这个地方需要什么吗？一些GDP！”。但我认为这是一项重要的举措，因为经济发展为国家提供了除<a href="https://criticallegalthinking.com/2016/01/20/fanon-on-violence-and-the-person/">宣泄暴力</a>之外的其他目的。确定长期愿景也有助于做出当前的领导力决策，因为它让人们可以问“哪些领导者将使我们更接近那个光明、繁荣的未来？”。</p><p>认为半个世纪后加沙可能成为一个经济繁荣的地方也并非不现实。 20世纪60年代和70年代，河内大片地区被<a href="https://www.salon.com/2022/12/11/the-christmas-bombing-of-1972--and-why-that-misremembered-vietnam-moment-matters/">美国炸弹夷为平地</a>，但五十年后，它看起来像这样： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F528a8495-7724-44a7-9258-09f839143b2e_1024x683.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F528a8495-7724-44a7-9258-09f839143b2e_1024x683.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F528a8495-7724-44a7-9258-09f839143b2e_1024x683.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F528a8495-7724-44a7-9258-09f839143b2e_1024x683.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F528a8495-7724-44a7-9258-09f839143b2e_1024x683.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F528a8495-7724-44a7-9258-09f839143b2e_1024x683.jpeg" width="694" height="462.892578125" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/528a8495-7724-44a7-9258-09f839143b2e_1024x683.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:683,&quot;width&quot;:1024,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:694,&quot;bytes&quot;:234297,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F528a8495-7724-44a7-9258-09f839143b2e_1024x683.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F528a8495-7724-44a7-9258-09f839143b2e_1024x683.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F528a8495-7724-44a7-9258-09f839143b2e_1024x683.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F528a8495-7724-44a7-9258-09f839143b2e_1024x683.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption"> “<a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?curid=112824732">河内夜景</a>”作者： <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?title=User:Ntml4507&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1">Ntml4507</a> ， <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/?ref=openverse">CC BY-SA 4.0</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>事实上，当今许多富裕国家在上个世纪的历史中都曾经历过因战争而蹂躏、因专制政府而步履蹒跚的时期。他们摆脱了那些困难时期，也许加沙也可以。</p><p>当然，这种发展需要民族自决、重大外部冲突的结束以及长期的政治稳定。我不确定现在有人知道如何为加沙获取这些东西。但我认为重要的是要了解可能带来的好处。</p><p>以下是加沙经济未来愿景的简要概述。它从一个定量目标开始：将按购买力平价计算的人均 GDP 提高到 10,000 美元。然后，我使用其他一些国家作为比较，推测加沙可以瞄准的一些行业。我会谈谈移民如何发挥重要作用。我并不是要把这一愿景作为一个独特的愿景来呈现——有很多替代方法和目标，而且无论如何，这都远不是一个详细的路线图。但我希望这篇文章足以引发人们对美好日子的思考。</p><h4>具体目标：将加沙人均 GDP (PPP) 提高到 10,000 美元</h4><p>许多人，尤其是政治领域的左翼人士，批评国内生产总值作为衡量人类福利的有用性。当然，GDP 遗漏了很多重要的东西（休闲、不平等、政治自由、预期寿命、教育等等）。但 GDP 与人类发展指数等更广泛的福祉指标以及 <a href="https://ourworldindata.org/grapher/median-daily-per-capita-expenditure-vs-gdp-per-capita">消费中位数水平</a><a href="https://ourworldindata.org/grapher/augmented-hdi-vs-gdp-per-capita">密切相关</a>。如果你增加GDP，你的国家很可能会变得更健康、寿命更长、吃得更好、受教育程度更高、更幸福等等。</p><p><a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/economic-possibilities-for-gaza">阅读更多</a></p>; 
