责</a>哈马斯的袭击。 “小队”呼吁以色列不要采取军事行动回应，这是极不现实的，但这并不构成对哈马斯的丝毫支持。多年来一直支持巴勒斯坦的伊丽莎白·沃伦（Elizabeth Warren）在听到有关哈马斯暴力行为的报道时<a href="https://twitter.com/JoshKraushaar/status/1711420664622592272">泪流满面</a>，她说：“我今天在这里明确表示，恐怖主义是没有任何理由的。”等等。一些纽约民主党<a href="https://twitter.com/bradlander/status/1711168969980166363">领导人</a>谴责<a href="https://www.nydailynews.com/2023/10/09/mayor-adams-says-dsa-backed-nyc-pols-must-soul-search-after-controversial-pro-palestine-rally-is-that-something-they-stand-for/">了</a>DSA 集会； AOC<a href="https://www.politico.com/news/2023/10/10/aoc-pro-palestine-nyc-rally-00120684">谴责</a>这次集会的“偏执和冷酷”。</p><p>即使在左翼草根阶层中，也没有一致赞扬哈马斯的战争罪行。一些有原则的社会主义者坚持正派： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04de7684-f173-4353-aae9-44de341f3886_905x274.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04de7684-f173-4353-aae9-44de341f3886_905x274.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04de7684-f173-4353-aae9-44de341f3886_905x274.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04de7684-f173-4353-aae9-44de341f3886_905x274.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04de7684-f173-4353-aae9-44de341f3886_905x274.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/imag